quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  77,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  77,1,qasam hai unn ( hawaon ) ki jo pay Dur pay bhaije jati hain
  77,2,phir tofani raftaar se chalti hain
  77,3,aur ( baadalon ko ) utha kar phailaati hain
  77,4,phir ( unn ko ) phaar kar judda karti hain
  77,5,phir ( dilon mein khuda ki ) yaad daalti hain
  77,6,izr ke tor par ya draway ke tor par
  77,7,jis cheez ka tum se wada kya ja raha hai woh zaroor waqay honay wali hai
  77,8,phir jab setaaray maand par jayen ge
  77,9,aur aasman phaar diya jaye ga
  77,10,aur pahar dhanak daaley jayen ge
  77,11,aur Rasolo-n ki haazri ka waqt aa puhanche ga ( is roz woh cheez waqay ho jaye gi )
  77,12,kis roz ke liye yeh kaam utha rakha gaya hai ?
  77,13,faislay ke roz ke liye
  77,14,aur tumhe kya khabar ke woh faislay ka din kya hai ?
  77,15,tabahi hai uss din jhutlanay walon ke liye
  77,16,kya hum ne uglo ko halaak nahi kya ?
  77,17,phir aُnhi ke peechay hum baad walon ko chalta karen ge
  77,18,mujrimon ke sath hum yahi kuch kya karte hain
  77,19,tabahi hai uss din jhutlanay walon ke liye
  77,20,kya hum ne aik haqeer pani se tumhe peda nahi kya
  77,21,"aur aik muqarara muddat taq ,"
  77,22,ussay aik mehfooz jagah tehra-ay rakha ?
  77,23,"to dekho, hum iss par Qadir thay, pas hum bohat achi qudrat rakhnay walay hain"
  77,24,tabahi hai uss roz jhutlanay walon ke liye
  77,25,kya hum ne zameen ko samaitt kar rakhnay wali nahi banaya
  77,26,zindon ke liye bhi aur mُrdon ke liye bhi
  77,27,"aur is mein buland o baala pahar jamaye, aur tumhe meetha pani pilaya ?"
  77,28,tabahi hai uss roz jhutlanay walon ke liye
  77,29,chalo ab usi cheez ki taraf jisay tum jhtlaya karte thay
  77,30,chalo uss saaye ki taraf jo teen shaakhon wala hai
  77,31,nah thandak pohanchanay wala aur nah aag ki lapat se bachanay wala
  77,32,woh aag mehal jaisi barri barri chingariya phainky gi
  77,33,( jo uchhalti hui yun mehsoos hon gi ) goya ke woh zard oont hain
  77,34,tabahi hai uss roz jhutlanay walon ke liye
  77,35,yeh woh din hai jis mein woh nah kuch bolein ge
  77,36,aur nah unhen mauqa diya jaye ga ke koi izr paish karen
  77,37,tabahi hai uss din jhutlanay walon ke liye
  77,38,yeh faislay ka din hai hum ne tumhe aur tum se pehlay guzray hue logon ko jama kar diya hai
  77,39,ab agar koi chaal tum chal satke ho to mere muqaabla mein chal dekho
  77,40,tabahi hai uss din jhutlanay walon ke liye
  77,41,mut-taqi log aaj saayon aur chashmon mein hain
  77,42,aur jo phal woh chahain ( unn ke liye haazir hain )
  77,43,khao aur piyo mazay se apne unn aamaal ke siilay mein jo tum karte rahay ho
  77,44,hum naik logon ko aisi hi jaza dete hain
  77,45,tabahi hai uss roz jhutlanay walon ke liye
  77,46,kha lau aur mazay kar lau thoray din haqeeqat mein tum log mujrim ho
  77,47,tabahi hai uss roz jhutlanay walon ke liye
  77,48,jab inn se kaha jata hai ke ( Allah ke agay ) jhuko to nahi jhukatey
  77,49,tabahi hai uss roz jhutlanay walon ke liye
  77,50,ab iss ( quran ) ke baad aur konsa kalaam aisa ho sakta hai jis par yeh imaan layein ?
